 shortfalls in aid disbursement? And what do these recent experiences suggest for improving the multilateral design, mobilization, and coordination of assistance to postconflict societies? Good intentions notwithstanding, inadequate preparation, poor coordination, and lack of perseverance can threaten the recovery of vulnerable polities whose collapse would endanger regional peace and security.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2023) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Peace.2bisacsh1 aAwartani, Hisham, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBall, Nicole, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBarnes, Sam, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBoyce, James K., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBratton, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrynen, Rex, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFoley, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aForman, Shepard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aForman, Shepard, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHertić, Zlatko, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLandsberg, Chris, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPatrick, Steward, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPatrick, Stewart, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPeou, Sorpong, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRosa, Herman, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWoodcraft, Clare, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWoodward, Susan L., econtributor.4ctb4http